fields.summary: Incorrect position of the Advanced Filter header
fields.description:
*Expected Position*
The Advanced Filter header should be placed above the Orderlist and the Status Overview tabs. See the attached image.

*Actual Position*
The Advanced Filter header is placed on the Orderlist tab.

resolution.name: Fixed
